# ⚙️ Installation

### 1. Clone the Repository

```
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/air-canvas.git
cd air-canvas
```

### 2. Install Dependencies

```
pip install opencv-python mediapipe numpy
```

Or install using a requirements file:

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

# ▶️ Usage

Run the main Python file:

```
python air_canvas.py
```

The webcam will open and the application will begin detecting hand gestures.

---

# 🎮 Controls

| Input                 | Action       |
| --------------------- | ------------ |
| Index Finger          | Draw         |
| Index + Middle Finger | Select Color |
| C                     | Clear Canvas |
| Q                     | Quit Program |

